text: Horalogium, Horarum breue inchoat en hic.OnVIII kalend Ianuariiþæt byð on cristes mæsse dæg byð seo sceadu to underne & to none seofon & twentigoþan healfes fotes & to middæge feower & twentig.
OnVIII idus Ianuariiþæt ys on þone twelftan dæg byð seo sceadu to underne & to noneXXVfota & to middægeXXII.
OnXII kalend Februariibið seo sceadu to underne & to none an & twentig fota & to middæge ehtatyne & lytle mare.
OnII non Februariibyð seo sceadu to underne & to none ehta teoþan healfes fotes & to middæge fiftyne.
OnXII kalend Martiibið seo sceadu to underne & to none fiftyne fota & to middæge twelfe.
OnII non Martiibið seo sceadu to underne & to none þreottyne fota & to middæge teoþan hielfes.
OnXII kalend Aprilisþæt is emnihte byð seo sceadu to underne & to none endlufon fota & to middæge nigoþan healfes.
Onnon Aprilisbið seo sceadu to underne & to none teoðan healfes fotes lang & to middæge forneah seofun.
OnXII kalend Maiibyð seo sceadu to underne & to none ehta fota & lytel eaca & to middæge forneah syx.
OnII non Maiibyþ seo sceadu to underne & to none forneah ehta fota & to middæge fiftan healfes.
OnXII kalend Iuniibið seo sceadu to underne & to none seofon fota & to middæge feower.
Onkalend Iuniibið seo sceadu to underne & to none lytle lengre þonne seofon fota & to middæge feower.
Onidus Iuniibið seo sceadu to underne & to none ehtoðan healfes fotes lang & to middæge feower.
OnVIII kalend IVLIþæt ys on Iohannes mæsse dæg bið seo sceadu to underne & to none wel neh ehta fota & to middægIIII.
OnII non IVLIbið seo sceadu to underne & to none eahta fota & to middæge lytle mare þonne feower.
OnXII kalend Agvstibið seo sceadu to underne & to none ehta fota & lytle mare & to middæge fiftan healfes.
OnVIII ID Agvstibið seo sceadu to underne & to none nigoþan healfes fotes lang & to middæge lytle mare þonneV.
Onduodecima kalend Septembrisbið seo sceadu to underne & to none nigun fota & to middæge syx.
Onnon Septembrisbið seo sceadu to underne & to none endleftan healfes fotes lang & to middæge seofon.
OnXII kalend Octobrisþæt ys emnihte bið seo sceadu to underne & to none twelf fota lang & to middæge nigun.
OnII non Octobrisbið seo sceadu to underne & to none feowertyne fota & to middæge endlufon.
OnXII kalend Novembrisbið seo sceadu to underne & to none syxtyne fota lang & lytle mare & to middægeXIII.
Onnon Novembrisbið seo sceadu to underne & to none nigontyne fota & lytle mare & to middæge seofontyne.
OnXII kalend Decembrisbið seo sceadu to underne & to none forneah feower &XXfota & to middæge an & twentig.
OnIIII none Decembrisbið seo sceadu to underne & to non syx &XXfota & to middæge þreo & twentig.
OnXIX kalend Ianuariibið seo sceadu to underne & to none seofon & twenti fota & to middæge fif & twentig forneah.
